column2: select q.id as id, round(p.ra,#) as ra, round(p.dec,#) as dec,  round(p.rowc,#) as rowc, round(p.extinction_r,#) as rExt, round(p.psfMag_u,#) as upsf, round(p.psfMag_g,#) as gpsf, round(p.psfMag_r,#) as rpsf, round(p.psfMag_i,#) as ipsf, round(p.psfMag_z,#) as zpsf, round(p.psfMagErr_u,#) as uErr, round(p.psfMagErr_g,#) as gErr, round(p.psfMagErr_r,#) as rErr, round(p.psfMagErr_i,#) as iErr, round(p.psfMagErr_z,#) as zErr, p.objID as objID2,   round(f.mjd_r, #) as mjd_r into mydb.MyTable from mydb.MyTable_harry q cross apply dr7.dbo.fGetNearbyObjAllEq(q.ra, q.dec, #) N, photoobj p, field f   where p.objID = N.objID and f.fieldID = p.fieldID and p.type = #
